{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["Distance Along Geometry"], "type": "title", "extent": [0, 28], "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "summary", "extent": [135, 247], "text": ["Measures the distance of the shortest path along the geometry\u2019s edges or surfaces from each start point."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [247, 370], "text": ["This node can be used to measure the distance along a surface, which is useful\nwhen masking operations based on distance."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [389, 563], "text": ["A subset of components in the input geometry whose attribute value will\n    be set.  Leave this blank to affect the attribute value for all components\n    in the input."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Group"], "role": "item", "extent": [382, 389], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [575, 607], "text": ["What the group is made of."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Group Type"], "role": "item", "extent": [563, 575], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [621, 665], "text": ["Start points to measure distance from."]}], "indent": 0, "text": ["Start Points"], "role": "item", "extent": [607, 621], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [682, 753], "text": ["Method for measuring each point\u2019s distance from the start points."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [763, 843], "text": ["The shortest distance from a start point following a path along edges."]}], "indent": 4, "type": "dt", "extent": [753, 763], "text": ["Edge"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [856, 1011], "text": ["The shortest distance from a start point following a path along the\n        surfaces of the input geometry, both along edges and across polygons."]}], "indent": 4, "type": "dt", "extent": [843, 856], "text": ["Surface"]}], "container": true, "type": "dt_group"}], "indent": 0, "tex